2009-11-29  Magnus Henoch  <magnus.henoch@gmail.com>

	* src/gui.c (gui_colorpicker_add, gui_colorpicker_set_color): Use
	GtkColorButton instead of gnome_color_picker.
	(gui_keybind): Use gtk_window_add_accel_group intead of
	gtk_accel_group_attach.
	(gui_text_area_add): Use GtkTextView instead of the deprecated
	GtkText.
	(gui_dialog_window): s/GTK_WINDOW_DIALOG/GTK_WINDOW_TOPLEVEL/

	* src/common.c (g_list_insert_before_element): Renamed from
	g_list_insert_before, as it conflicts with an added GList
	function.
	* src/common.h (G_LIST_INSERT_BEFORE_ELEMENT): Renamed from
	G_LIST_INSERT_BEFORE.
	* src/dialog.c (csdialog_wpattern_clist_row_move_cb)
	(csdialog_wpattern_new_color_selection_cb): Update callers.

	* lib/gnome-dateedit.c (gnome_date_edit_class_init): Use
	GTK_CLASS_TYPE instead of accessing type member.  Remove call to
	gtk_object_class_add_signals.

	* lib/Makefile.am: Remove gnome-color-picker, as we use the
	builtin GtkColorButton now.
	* lib/gnome-color-picker.c: Remove.
	* lib/gnome-color-picker.h: Remove.
	* lib/README.gnome: Remove mention of gnome-color-picker.

	* configure.in: Use pkg-config to check for gtk+-2.0 and
	gtkgl-2.0.  Remove older tests.

	* intl/*: Remove; can be generated by autopoint.

	* po/*: Remove those files that can be generated.

	* */Makefile.in: Remove (generated).

	* debug/Makefile.am (AM_CFLAGS): Changed from INCLUDES.

	* configure.in: Update to newer initialisation forms.  Add
	description to all AC_DEFINEs.  Add AM_GNU_GETTEXT_VERSION.

	* configure: Remove (generated).

	* config.h.in: Remove (generated).

	* aclocal.m4: Remove (generated).

	* acconfig.h: Remove; using newer AC_DEFINE construct instead.

	* Makefile.am (ACLOCAL_AMFLAGS): Add by gettext recommendation.

	* ABOUT-NLS: Update to gettext 0.17.

	* .hgignore: Ignore generated files.

0.9 (9 September 1999)
----------------------

* Initial release.
